==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Siphonarid
<hw>Si`pho*na"rid</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any one of numerous species of limpet-shaped pulmonate gastropods
of the genus <gen>Siphonaria</gen>. They cling to rocks between high and
low water marks and have both lunglike organs and gills.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Si`pho*na"rid</wf>, <pos>a.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Siphonata</ent>⟦br⟧
